    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "45 mins seems okay but what if the LNER is running late or there's a strike or something? i'm a bit nervous about stuff going wrong with the connection. are there any other common things that mess up these kinds of transfers?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
